{% comment %}
  ternyata · TRMNL full (800x480, e-ink N&B)
  Source : /api/term (polling, single URL => clés à la racine).
  Concept : on lit le synopsis en bahasa, on devine le film, on vérifie en bas
  (title_bar = la réponse). Sous le synopsis, 3 mots de vocabulaire (kosakata).
  Design : composants natifs TRMNL, monochrome haute densité, zéro illustration.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="view view--full">
  <div class="layout" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:100%;">

    <!-- ============ HEADER ============ -->
    <div style="padding-bottom:10px;border-bottom:4px solid var(--color-black,#000);">
      <span class="label label--small" style="text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:3px;">
        Film du jour · {{ film_date_label }}
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ SYNOPSIS (héros) ============ -->
    <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;min-height:0;padding:14px 0;">
      {% for line in synopsis_lines %}
        <div style="font-size:29px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.34;">{{ line }}</div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <!-- ============ KOSAKATA (3 mots) ============ -->
    <div style="border-top:3px solid var(--color-black,#000);padding-top:10px;">
      <span class="label label--small" style="text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:3px;">Kosakata</span>
      <div style="margin-top:6px;">
        {% for v in vocab %}
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:14px;padding:2px 0;">
            <span style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;min-width:240px;letter-spacing:-0.3px;">
              {{ v.word }}<span style="font-size:16px;font-weight:400;margin-left:6px;">{{ v.pos }}</span>
            </span>
            <span style="font-size:22px;">{{ v.gloss }}</span>
          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============ TITLE BAR (la réponse) ============ -->
    <div class="title_bar" style="margin-top:6px;">
      <img class="image" src="https://trmnl.com/images/plugins/trmnl--render.svg" />
      <span class="title">
        {{ film.title }}{% if film.director %} · {{ film.director }}{% endif %}{% if film.year %}, {{ film.year }}{% endif %}
      </span>
      {% if generated_at_label %}<span class="instance">MAJ {{ generated_at_label }}</span>{% endif %}
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
